Official mirror from qucs SVN, hosted on:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/qucs

Compile instructions Linux (Ubuntu):
First make sure you have all packages installed:
build-essential flex bison qt4-dev-tools gperf

Install ADMS 2.3.0:

svn checkout svn://svn.code.sf.net/p/qucs/code/trunk/adms-2.3.0 adms-2.3.0
./configure
make
sudo make install 
sudo ldconfig

Compile qucs:
cd qucs
./autogen.sh
make
sudo make install


Compile qucs-core:
cd qucs-core
./autogen.sh
make
sudo make install
